{"tid":1343441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港自衛軍，正式成立了","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T21:14:37.000Z","uid":89419,"like":116,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"43d334b23fb42093f01c081fab8caf3d24e79316","tid":1343441,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:46:42.000Z","msg":"我諗唔到有咩理由再唔勇武<br />\n頭先仲見到有人話200萬人入元朗<br />\n<strong>有撚用咩</strong><br />\n行左成兩個月<br />\n政府嘅回應都係得<strong>吹呀</strong>兩隻字<br />\n經過今晚<br />\n香港警察已經正式宣佈與民為敵<br />\n要保護自己，保護身邊人<br />\n唯有自建防衛軍<br />\n成立香港國<br />\n同時真真正正爭取外國支持<br />\n如果到呢一刻仲希望用和理非可以打動到港共嘅<br />\n你跟本就係幫兇<br />\n你地都間接一棍一棍咁打喺其他香港人身上<br />\n希望泛民，和理非可以動用你地嘅影響力<br />\n實實在在咁幫下香港<br />\n記住 我地已經退無可退了<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"097dcf8eb068f63a20ae63467fc3613187d8a9c8","tid":1343441,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:47:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3afef428b47ba9b073c0a645e0a0a8a8f07bf17f","tid":1343441,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571ceb2aad32b9a82df6fa63f73ac9e0fb818167","tid":1343441,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:48:16.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"2d7625e54b68cebacc708b835956cde2f032b985","tid":1343441,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927d86658a6919b298f3f682a0a6f637bf05e6f0","tid":1343441,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d334b23fb42093f01c081fab8caf3d24e79316","tid":1343441,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:46:42.000Z","msg":"我諗唔到有咩理由再唔勇武<br />\n頭先仲見到有人話200萬人入元朗<br />\n<strong>有撚用咩</strong><